An interesting theory of gaming is that you need to 
Condition the players of a game to play the game in 
The way the game is fun. 
In this video, he talks a bit about how Bloodborn made
People love Dark Souls more due to how it forced
Players to fight in melee without a fully protective 
Shield, while having mechanics to make sure that actions 
Are fast enough that it is not annoying to players.

https://youtu.be/AC3OuLU5XCw
